answer: Cumulative fines imposed on OMICS Publishing Group in 2019 from multiple FTC investigations into alleged anticompetitive conduct in the scholarly publishing industry (IDs: 1390612, 1367080, 1377646, 1365224, 2006659, 1340994, 1376553, 1364328, 1378987, 1635088, 1408128) were in the millions of dollars, totalling over $50 million dollars.
